message: Fixed bug that allowed for XSS attacks
Added feature detection and performance improvements

v0.2.0
- Data reactivity and automatically updating UI
- Support for nested components
- Shared state support (with data reactivity!)
- Custom attribute exceptions for your templates
Add check for infinite loops on nested components

v0.2.2
Reassigned methods to Component.prototype. Had accidentally attached them to the Object.prototype.
Updated style handling for better browser support
Fixed bug that was causing sanitizer to not run

v3.0.0
- Removed native sanitization in favor of BYO
- Added hooks to add global and component-specific sanitization callbacks

v4.0.0
- Data is once again automatically encoded to help protect you from cross-site scripting (XSS) attacks.
- Changes to diffing and rendering reduce reflows and improve performance.
- Support pushed back even further to IE9.
- *Deprecated:* Custom sanitizer methods were removed in favor of built-in, automated HTML encoding. You can still add custom sanitization within template functions.
Switched from filter() + map() to reduce() for better performance
Added extra check for style mapping
Fixed bug with properties not updating
Better account for collapsing spaces in diffing
Fixed issue with attributes on SVGs
Added check for readonly properties when setting/removing attributes
Allow empty properties and attached events
Fix bug that prevent styles from being injected into the DOM

Fixed issue with certain properties not being removed properly
https://github.com/cferdinandi/reef/issues/28
Fixed DOM map issue with dynamic properties

Added bugfix for form properties getting stripped away
https://github.com/cferdinandi/reef/issues/33
Allow value to be set from data
patched inconsistencies in select element behavior
New build process, updated filenaming structure
Run render after updating entire state
Added missing reactivity for deleting properties
Only run update if value changes
Check for focus before setting tabindex on headings
Fixed bug that was breaking URLs in CSS properties
Fixed bug that ignored inputs with a value of 0
Fixed falsy value check on properties
Fixed issue with routes order and home
Fixed lack of delete property polyfill support

Fix typo in package.json

The `browser["reef-es"]` property was set to `"./dist/reef.cjs.min.js"`. It should be `"./dist/reef.es.min.js"`.
Fixed sanitizing bug and added element to template() args
Allow raw HTML in specific elements in a component
Fixed falsy check on reef-* attributes
Fix issue with defaults and replaced nodes
Added a more surgical DOM update https://github.com/cferdinandi/reef/issues/56
Added ReefSnorkel and a bunch of new custom events
Fixed type not defined error in router
Fixed sanitization bug that allowed javascript in links
Fixed performance issues and recursion bug
Added proper type checking in proxy
Fixed issue with form field IDs when comparing if nodes are a different type
Added a before-render event and setter methods
replace custom deep copy method with structuredClone()
Added listeners class for capturing events
Added support for safe on* event listeners
bugfix: Check for events object before grabbing properties
Fixed but with listeners() that would strip out other attributes
Added support for arguments on event listeners
Setup demo, ran build, rebased project.
Fixed issue with multiple event listeners - https://github.com/cferdinandi/reef/issues/200
